    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cantilevered masonry blocks used singly or in ranges to support architectural or ornamental features or used in successive courses to form arches, domes, or vaults; when referring generally to the projecting courses of masonry, prefer "oversailing courses."</Note_Text>
